{"tid":582432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【撐女性變出醜】名校畢業生愛瑪屈臣妙麗 手上紋身文法有錯","createTime":"2018-03-06T07:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T11:21:36.000Z","uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0642fe42dc46339c634957e0362e106688358fce","tid":582432,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/152137_bc60a464c4444cf5cf8814b96eebb67c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F152137_bc60a464c4444cf5cf8814b96eebb67c.png&h=f11badd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/152138_e28396bdd608df7b1cf256c32d7a3af6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F152138_e28396bdd608df7b1cf256c32d7a3af6.png&h=81b36ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/152139_b8fa101dcf5310575bfba814518c43aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F152139_b8fa101dcf5310575bfba814518c43aa.png&h=bfcee7cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國女星愛瑪屈臣（Emma Watson）噚出盛裝出席奧斯卡嘅會後派對，畢業於名牌大學布朗大學（Brown University）嘅佢係圈中有名嘅高材生，但佢手上嘅紋身就似乎唔啱文法，引來網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n佢於派對前大方展示手上紋身，雖然相信只係印水紙，但上面寫上嘅撐女性反性騷擾標語「Time's Up」就被發現文法有錯，爭咗個撇號，變成「Times Up」，認真失禮。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180306/57910778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180306%2F57910778&d=7Q2v0T3c8BHQ%2B9PZjLsvqzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=de73ccc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180306%2F57910778&h=4e17d0ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180306/57910778</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩係差一點，亦都好彩係貼紙嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw, 妙麗個樣真係老咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95e81164a271bfbff5418b776b1c075dbd625eb","tid":582432,"uid":24345,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"個髮型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8962c1235ca3003b049b9ac5a4a3e374d569838d","tid":582432,"uid":64073,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"e95e81164a271bfbff5418b776b1c075dbd625eb","tid":582432,"uid":24345,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"個髮型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:40:58.000Z","msg":"用自己個樣嚟反性侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb19769fedf2245aa2b9eb4c4fb9fb1c82418e8","tid":582432,"uid":122261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8962c1235ca3003b049b9ac5a4a3e374d569838d","tid":582432,"uid":64073,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"e95e81164a271bfbff5418b776b1c075dbd625eb","tid":582432,"uid":24345,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"個髮型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:40:58.000Z","msg":"用自己個樣嚟反性侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi